<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-12-12T15:24:30-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-12-12T15:24:30-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T15:24:30-05:00</updated><title> Apple 的新 iPhone 安全设置可防止窃贼侵入您的数字帐户</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手中的 iPhone 15 Pro。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qdOBKmL-4rFSQg5xEHY8rEqy0Ug=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72956741/236792_iPhone_15_Pro_and_15_Pro_Max _product_photos_AJohnson_0005.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Allison Johnson / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;2Iw8Gz&quot;>;Apple 正在让 iPhone 窃贼在掌握了您设备的密码后更难访问您的个人信息。据&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wsj.com/tech/personal-tech/apple-iphone-ios-update-stolen-device-protection-698d760e&quot;>;《华尔街日报》报道&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;，Apple 在其 iOS 17.3 测试版中加入了新的被盗设备保护功能，启用后，需要通过 Face ID 或 Touch ID 进行身份验证才能执行某些操作。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;c3kNTO&quot;>;新功能似乎是为了回应 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-iphone-setting-thieves-use-to-lock-you-out-of-your 中提出的担忧-apple-account-716d350d&quot;>;上一页&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-iphone-security-theft-passcode-data-privacya-basic-iphone-feature- 《华尔街日报》的 help-criminals-steal-your-digital-life-cbf14b1a&quot;>;报道&lt;/a>;描述了窃贼如何看着受害者输入 iPhone 密码，然后窃取他们的设备。这使得窃贼能够访问设备上存储的大量个人和财务信息，从而将受害者锁定在其 iCloud 帐户之外，并使用... 花费数千美元...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998665/apple-stolen-device-protection-face-touch-id-icloud-account-vulnerability-ios-17-3-beta&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998665/apple-stolen-device-protection-face-touch-id-icloud-account-vulnerability-ios-17-3-beta" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998665/apple-stolen-device-protection-face-touch-id-icloud-account-vulnerability-ios-17-3-beta</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T14:33:19-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T14:33:19-05:00</updated><title> Netflix 透露了我们观看《夜间特工》和《夏洛特女王》的时间</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Netflix 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BV6sHB3TFNGH2orTnZv9f-ggTH4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/72956600/STK072_VRG_Illo_N_Barclay_8_netflix.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Nick Barclay / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;BLkjYc&quot;>;Netflix 将开始发布两次新报告详细介绍该平台上最受欢迎的节目和电影的一年。今天发布的第一份报告详细介绍了 2023 年 1 月至 6 月观看次数最多的内容，这或许是迄今为止最好的了解人们实际观看 Netflix 庞大影片库的人数的报告。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rBXY67&quot; >;“我们观看的内容：Netflix 参与度报告”将跟踪三个指标：观看时长、节目是否在全球范围内播放以及节目的发布日期。在第一份报告中，&lt;em>;夜间特工&lt;/em>; 第一季以超过 8.12 亿小时的观看时间位居榜首，其次是&lt;em>;Ginny &amp;amp;amp; 。 Georgia&lt;/em>;&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;第二季（观看时间为 6.651 亿小时）、&lt;em>;荣耀&lt;/em>;第一季&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;（观看时间为 6.228 亿小时）、 &lt;em>;周三&lt;/em>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998533/netflix-what-we-watched -report-data-popular&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998533/netflix-what-we-watched-report-data-popular" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998533/netflix-what-we-watched-report-data-popular</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T14:17:14-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T14:17:14-05:00</updated><title> Tim Sweeney 谈 Epic 战胜 Google</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Tim Sweeney 在 Google 和 Epic 徽标前的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hcu8fGqWLJkX2lW6I2RYJCino18=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72956528/236883_Epic_Vs_Google_10_CVirginia .0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 提供 |摄影：Philip Pacheco，Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Epic 获胜。该诉讼的架构师有何看法？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23996474/epic-tim-sweeney-interview-win-google-antitrust-lawsuit-district-court &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23996474/epic-tim-sweeney-interview-win-google-antitrust-lawsuit-district-court" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23996474/epic-tim-sweeney-interview-win-google-antitrust-lawsuit-district-court</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T13:38:50-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T13:38:50-05:00</updated><title> WhatsApp 的新固定消息让您可以轻松地在任务中保持群聊</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;WhatsApp 固定消息功能的宣传图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ezPKKIOq0Y7SylDcSrMeDkHQOEU=/149x0:1771x1081/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72956382/WhatsApp_Pinned_Messages_Editorial_1920x1080 .0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;WhatsApp 首次推出固定消息。&lt;/em>; |图片：WhatsApp&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;YLEYCd&quot;>;WhatsApp 正在添加将消息固定到聊天顶部的功能，有效期最长为 30 天。 Meta 表示，其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/help/messenger-app/1335189030292814&quot;>;移动 Facebook Messenger 应用&lt;/a>; 已具备该功能，现已向用户推出，所以并不是每个人都会立即看到它。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;JfYOJF&quot;>;Meta 表示，用户需要长按消息并点击“Pin”。 7 天是 PIN 的默认持续时间，但用户可以选择将其更改为 24 小时或 30 天。任何消息都可以固定，因此如果您想固定民意调查、图片甚至视频，都可以。群聊管理员也可以将 pin 设置为仅对其他管理员可见。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：WhatsApp&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;每个消息应用程序都应该有此功能。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zxdjXf&quot;>;此功能正在请求添加到所有直接消息传递中...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998425/whatsapp-pin-messages-meta-encrypted-messaging-chats&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998425/whatsapp-pin-messages-meta-encrypted-messaging-chats" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998425/whatsapp-pin-messages-meta-encrypted-messaging-chats</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T13:38:13-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T13:38:13-05:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的电子书阅读器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色背景下空中漂浮的各种物体&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ahl9GA-W3_l8GrBRn3vh1DQwhUU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72396035/236754_Best_ebook_readers_for_2023_WJoel.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Will Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从在浴缸里读书到在浴缸里乱写乱画从深入亚马逊生态系统到彻底避开它，每个人都有一款电子阅读器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-读者&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T13:30:54-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T13:30:54-05:00</updated><title>新的《神秘博士》首映感觉就像是一记及时的耳光</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个非常接近褪色的黑人，穿着一件白色纽扣衬衫，脖子上系着一条解开的领带。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/DcXYUi0CWeglcCiZgkJf0lwZczI=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72956344/dw_sp3_tg_059_08c7c12c。 0.jpeg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：BBC&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;拉塞尔·T·戴维斯 (Russell T. Davies) 的心是在正确的地方，但努蒂·盖特瓦 (Ncuti Gatwa) 的新神秘博士的推出却充满了许多可疑的决定和种族主义比喻。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23996697/doctor-who-the-giggle-bi Generation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23996697/doctor-who-the-giggle-bigeneration" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23996697/doctor-who-the-giggle-bi Generation</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T13:21:25-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T13:21:25-05:00</updated><title>二合一：TP-Link 两大智能家居品牌终于用同一款应用</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_gy1JfxDiWmkQH3g-zPHy_PYnDA=/0x1:752x502/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /72956311/426fe4779ef84210be35bf25cfe8df3d.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Tapo 和 Kasa 智能家居设备的用户现在可以在一个应用程序中控制它们。&lt;/em>; |图片：TP-Link&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;CNFChp&quot;>;Wi-Fi 路由器制造商 TP-Link 最终将其两个智能家居品牌整合到一个应用程序 Tapo 下。该公司自 2019 年以来一直在生产智能设备，但令人困惑的是，它们有两个不同的品牌：&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tapo.com/us/&quot;>;Tapo&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.kasasmart.com/us&quot;>;Kasa&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;o7b8Kw&quot;>;两个品牌都提供非常好的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899810/best-smart-plugs&quot;>;智能插头&lt;/a>;、开关、 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/9/17/23357060/tp-link-tapo-l930-review-apple-home-smart-lighting&quot;>;灯&lt;/a>;，已连接 &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911395/tp-link-tapo-wire-free-magcam-security-camera-price-specs&quot;>;相机&lt;/a>;，以及其他小工具的价格相对较低。但令人困惑的是，其中许多的外观和工作方式几乎相同，但需要两个单独的应用程序来控制它们。这种状况&lt;a href=&quot;https://community.tp-link.com/en/home/forum/topic/183058&quot;>;长期对这些廉价设备的用户感到沮丧&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt; p id=&quot;BcQVH7&quot;>;最近更新 (Tapo 3.0) 后，TP-Link 现在允许用户 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https% 3A%2F%2Fwww.tp-link.com%2Fus%2Fsupport%2Ffaq%2F3614%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F12%2F12%2F23998415% 2Ftp-link-smart-home-kasa-tapo-app-merge&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;将其 Kasa 设备移植到 Tapo 应用中&lt;/a>;。这使您可以通过一个应用程序控制所有设备，并将它们集成到您拥有的任何例程或自动化中...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/ 12/23998415/tp-link-smart-home-kasa-tapo-app-merge&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998415/tp-link-smart-home-kasa-tapo-app-merge" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/12/23998415/tp-link-smart-home-kasa-tapo-app-merge</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T12:41:12-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T12:41:12-05:00</updated><title> USDS 负责人 Mina Hsiang 希望大型科技公司最优秀的人才帮助修复政府</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;USDS 管理员 Mina Hsiang 的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/PWvCe4sSHHCZzoDADvgUoihjMSk=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72956135/Mina_Hsiang.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Alex Parkin / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;healthcare.gov 推出十年后，美联储的技术咨询公司希望您帮助解决下一件大事。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23997640/usds-mina-hsiang-white-house-obama-big-tech-government-decoder-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23997640/usds-mina-hsiang-white-house-obama-big-tech-government-decoder-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23997640/usds-mina-hsiang-white-house-obama-big-tech-government-decoder-interview</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-12T12:10:27-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-12T12:10:27-05:00</updated><title>如果说赛博卡车对行人来说是致命的，那是因为所有大型卡车都</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;特斯拉 Cyber​​truck 外面&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lik1Wfg_YJllg7sh0J5WQSl3_YA=/0x168:4032x2856/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/72956028/IMG_0618.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Parker Ortolani / Th